{"tid":1724894,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人諗過暫時拉攏警隊 倒戈政府施壓爭取普選？","createTime":"2019-11-15T14:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T19:02:17.000Z","uid":110975,"like":2,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"478de6a2a509aec3c963940052343786fbc51047","tid":1724894,"uid":110975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:58:32.000Z","msg":"其實清算警隊係未來一定會發生既事，只係依家政府為咗自保不能與警隊割所以先無限包庇。<br />\n<br />\n即係政府而家最怕我哋分化警隊向佢哋倒戈，敵人最怕嘅嘢就係我哋要做嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以有冇人諗過組織活動暫時拉攏警隊倒戈向政府施壓？<br />\n<br />\n例如組織一個「警民同行 爭取普選」遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時其他訴求爭取完 真真正正落實香港人嘅普選 <br />\n到時主權在民，我哋先再慢慢清算黑警都未遲<br />\n君子報仇 十年未晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知一定會有人出嚟屌小弟係散水撚 風向撚 鍵盤撚<br />\n只係分享下我嘅諗法 睇下大家覺得可唔可行<br />\n有錯隨便屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4afd04ba46892d7e80aef1c11730e61e06126c91","tid":1724894,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:59:35.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n韓國戰線要人呀！！完全冇人簽<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5f87a206af7d43d8336de66b36e526f98a7261f6","tid":1724894,"uid":771,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:00:44.000Z","msg":"天真<br />\n<br />\n一個白警都冇出現過<br />\n<br />\non 撚 9 諗法"},{"pid":"024d3e3bc29eea32b8ed78e681b7b9d008525568","tid":1724894,"uid":2656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:00:50.000Z","msg":"唔想講,拉"},{"pid":"da4243235919f1fc9a92e1207808412d59313437","tid":1724894,"uid":107405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:03:04.000Z","msg":"Popo彩你都on9<img 